name: Agog 14 Scribble Back Yellow
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D scribble sculpture colourful lines. It was at the back of my Agog VR world, hence the name. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
